  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Track and hunt bunnies in the woods with your bow. It’s what the King demands.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3515620/extras/87fbfefcf112e4803749ad8fbb17f082.poster.avif?t=1767848745\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3515620/extras/87fbfefcf112e4803749ad8fbb17f082.webm?t=1767848745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3515620/extras/87fbfefcf112e4803749ad8fbb17f082.mp4?t=1767848745\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Load the catapult and hurl them into the castle. No one will thank you.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3515620/extras/4c8c73d98707a1c8e6ed009a0538d5bb.poster.avif?t=1767848745\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3515620/extras/4c8c73d98707a1c8e6ed009a0538d5bb.webm?t=1767848745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3515620/extras/4c8c73d98707a1c8e6ed009a0538d5bb.mp4?t=1767848745\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Things tend to get stranger… and far more dangerous.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3515620/extras/6a2a9f9591ff10b0c2553a64c5c2fbf1.poster.avif?t=1767848745\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3515620/extras/6a2a9f9591ff10b0c2553a64c5c2fbf1.webm?t=1767848745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3515620/extras/6a2a9f9591ff10b0c2553a64c5c2fbf1.mp4?t=1767848745\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Do you think you can satisfy the King's desires? He’s not known for his mercy.</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >IN BUNNY HURLING, YOU CAN...</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move stealthily and wait for the perfect moment to <strong>shoot your arrow!</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lure the bunnies with a <strong>bunny caller</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beware of <strong>vengeful creatures and ghosts</strong>! You're not the only predator in the forest!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Freely explore a vast <strong>non-linear map</strong>, full of bunny curiosities and much more!</p></li></ul>",
