5\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3515620/extras/6a2a9f9591ff10b0c2553a64c5c2fbf1.mp4?t=1767848745\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Do you think you can satisfy the King's desires? He’s not known for his mercy.</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >IN BUNNY HURLING, YOU CAN...</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move stealthily and wait for the perfect moment to <strong>shoot your arrow!</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lure the bunnies with a <strong>bunny caller</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beware of <strong>vengeful creatures and ghosts</strong>! You're not the only predator in the forest!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Freely explore a vast <strong>non-linear map</strong>, full of bunny curiosities and much more!</p></li></ul>",
